  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate the Pharmacokinetics, Safety, and Tolerability of Intravenous Brivaracetam in Subjects &gt;= 1 Month to &lt; 16 Years of Age With Epilepsy</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Open-Label Study to Evaluate the Pharmacokinetics, Safety, and Tolerability of Intravenous Brivaracetam in Subjects &gt;= 1 Month &lt; 16 Years of Age With Epilepsy</official_title>
