  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to evaluate the pharmacokinetics (PK), safety, and tolerability
      of brivaracetam (BRV) administered intravenously (iv) in subjects &gt;= 1 month to &lt; 16 years of
      age with epilepsy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
